radius-engine
------------------------------------------
Radius Engine is a Lua script-based real-time 2D graphics engine designed for
rapidly prototyping games. Built on top of SDL and OpenGL, games made with
Radius Engine are portable to both Windows and Linux.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.0.1-1
  cygwin-devel-2.0.1-1
  libGL-devel-10.3.7-1
  libGL1-10.3.7-1
  libGLU-devel-9.0.0-1
  libGLU1-9.0.0-1
  libphysfs-devel-2.0.3-1bl2
  libphysfs1-2.0.3-1bl2
  libpng-devel-1.6.17-1
  libpng16-1.6.17-1
  libradius-engine-devel-1.1-1bl2
  libradius-engine0-1.1-1bl2
  libSDL-devel-1.2.15-2
  libSDL1.2_0-1.2.15-2
  libSDL_sound-devel-1.0.3-13
  libSDL_sound1.0_1-1.0.3-13
  libX11-devel-1.6.3-1
  libX11-xcb-devel-1.6.3-1
  libXau-devel-1.0.8-1
  libxcb-devel-1.10-1
  libxcb-glx-devel-1.10-1
  libXdamage-devel-1.1.4-1
  libXdmcp-devel-1.1.2-1
  libXext-devel-1.3.3-1
  libXfixes-devel-5.0.1-1
  lua-5.1.5-1
  zlib-devel-1.2.8-3

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.25-1
  cygport-0.18.1-1
  gcc-core-4.9.2-3
  libtool-2.4.6-1
  make-4.1-1

Canonical website:
  http://radius-engine.sf.net/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/radius-engine/radius-engine-1.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack radius-engine-1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./radius-engine-1.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/radius-engine-1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/radius-engine-1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libradius-engine0-1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libradius-engine-devel-1.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(radius-engine)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/radius-engine.README
  /usr/share/doc/radius-engine/ChangeLog

(libradius-engine0)
  /usr/bin/cygradius-engine-0.dll

(libradius-engine-devel)
  /usr/include/radius.h
  /usr/lib/libradius-engine.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/radius-engine.pc

